Class ContractorsTabularViewPanel

java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class ContractorsTabularViewPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

Displays a list of contractors in a tabular view.

The number of columns to display and their labels can be configured by setColumnsConfig(suncertify.ui.client.ContractorsTabularViewPanel.ColumnConfig[]) or by passing columns configuration array through constructor. Passing empty list to setContractors(Collection) will clear the table.
getSelectedContractor() returns the currently selected contractor in table. Change of selected contractor can be caught by adding a property change listener to listen on property selectedContractor.

Author:
Mohammad S. Abdellatif
